Class Dispatcher

java.lang.Object
java.rmi.server.RemoteObject
java.rmi.server.RemoteServer
java.rmi.server.UnicastRemoteObject
com.gateway.Dispatcher
All Implemented Interfaces:
DispatcherInt, Serializable, Remote
public class Dispatcher extends UnicastRemoteObject implements DispatcherInt
Represents a Dispatcher responsible for managing URL queues and processing. Implements the DispatcherInt interface.
